<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.205647>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Acarochelopodia caissara sp. nov.: A, idiosoma of female in dorsal view; B, same in ventral view; C, gnathosoma of female in ventral view; D, palp of female in lateral view; E, Genital area of female; F, leg I of female in lateral view; G, leg IV of female in lateral view; H, leg III of female in lateral view; I, leg II of male in medial view. Scale bars: A – B = 25 μm; C – I = 10 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/205647/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

